# Universal Gitignore for Full Stack Portfolio

# Secrets
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Dependency Folders
**/node_modules/
**/bower_components/

# Build & Project Outputs
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.vite/
**/.next/
**/.cache/
**/out/

# Infrastructure/Cloud
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/docker-compose.override.yml
**/.github/workflows/*.yml.example

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/*.log

# OS/System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# VS Code / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
